'''Melchior Ndadaye''' (n. [[Intara ya Muramvya| Murama]], [[28 Werurwe]] ya [[1953]] - [[Bujumbura]], [[21 Ukwakira]] ya [1993]]) yari [[umunyabwenge]] na [[umunyapolitiki]] [[Burundi| Burundian]] wabaye uwa kane [[Umugereka: Abategetsi b’Uburundi| Perezida wa Repubulika y’Uburundi]] kuva [[10 Nyakanga]] kuva [[1993]] kugeza yiciwe ku ya [21 Ukwakira]] muri uwo mwaka. Yabaye umukuru wa mbere w’ibihugu by’Uburundi ukomoka [[abahutu]], ubwoko bwinshi mu gihugu cye, akaba na perezida wa mbere [[Amatora y’umukuru w’igihugu cya Burundi yo mu 1993| yatowe mu buryo bwa demokarasi mu matora ataziguye]] mu [[amateka y’Uburundi]] .

Ndadaye yaje ku butegetsi biturutse ku kugwa kwa leta ya gisirikare iyobowe n’amoko mato [[Abatutsi]] mu rwego rw’inzibacyuho ya demokarasi yakozwe na Perezida [[Pierre Buyoya]], mu rwego rwo kubuza igihugu kugira a [[Intambara y'abanyarwanda | Ndadaye yatsinze Buyoya, umukandida w’ishyaka rimwe kugeza icyo gihe [[Ubumwe bw’iterambere ry’igihugu | UPRONA]], mu matora ya [[1 Kamena]] ya [[1993]] nk'umukandida wa [[Front for Democracy in I Burundi | FRODEBU]]. urubuga = Los Angeles Times | uwatangaje = Los Angeles Times | accessdate = 14 Mutarama 2015}} </ref> Ndadaye yagerageje gukora politiki ishyize mu gaciro igamije gushaka entente hagati y’amoko yombi. Icyakora, ntabwo yari ishyigikiwe n’imirenge ikaze [[abahutu]], bakomeje ibikorwa byo guhungabanya umutekano n’inyeshyamba na nyuma ya guverinoma ishingiye kuri demokarasi, kandi na yo yagombaga guhangana n’abatavuga rumwe n’ingabo z’igihugu, ndetse no muri amaboko y'abatutsi, bakekaga ivugurura ryabo.

Nyuma y'amezi atatu gusa Ndadaye yimitswe, ku ya 21 Ukwakira, habaye [[Coup d'etat mu Burundi yo mu 1993 | yagerageje guhirika ubutegetsi]], Nadadye asimburwa na [[François Ngeze]] nk'umuyobozi ya leta '' de facto ''. Kuri uwo munsi, perezida yajyanywe ku biro mu kigo cya gisirikare, aho yiciwe amaraso. <Ref name = coup> {{cite book | iheruka = ​​Krueger | mbere = Robert | iheruka2 = Krueger | ubanza2 = Kathleen Tobin | umutwe = Kuva kumena amaraso kugeza ibyiringiro muburundi: Imyaka ya Ambasade yacu mugihe cya Jenoside | uwatangaje = Itangazamakuru rya kaminuza ya Texas | itariki = 2007 | ahantu = | url = https: //www.sahistory.org. isbn = 9780292714861 | ref = harv}} </ref> Nubwo amaherezo ihirikwa ry’ubutegetsi ryatsinzwe kandi guverinoma ishingiye ku itegekonshinga ikomeza guhagarara, iyicwa rya Ndadaye ryateje ubukana bwa politiki hagati y’amoko yombi, bitangiza [[Intambara y’abaturage Burundi | Intambara y'abenegihugu mu Burundi]], izakomeza kugeza [[2005]]. <Ref name = coup />
